奧拉<ref>{{cite news|title=印度宣称研制首款隐形无人轰炸机 重达15吨2015首飞|url=http://mil.huanqiu.com/world/2012-06/2822329.html|date=2012-06-15|accessdate=2016-07-17|archive-date=2019-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811161402/http://mil.huanqiu.com/world/2012-06/2822329.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref group="注">也有中文網站譯為「輝光」，惟該詞無法查證，估計其名稱源於代號「AURA」的梵語譯文，從而得出輝光一詞，不過此非正確做法，印度官方也未就該無人機給予梵語名稱。</ref>（[[英語|英語]]：Autonomous Unmanned Research Aircraft，AURA）是[[國防研究及發展組織|印度國防研究與開發組織]]（DRDO）為[[印度空軍|印度空軍]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/india-to-develop-unmanned-combat-aerial-vehicle/105939-3.html |title=India to develop unmanned combat aerial vehicle |publisher=Ibnlive.in.com |date= |accessdate=2012-01-28 |archive-date=2013-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131010044302/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/india-to-develop-unmanned-combat-aerial-vehicle/105939-3.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://www.aviationweek.com/Article.aspx?id=/article-xml/AW_07_16_2012_p45-471464.xml New Imagery Details Indian Aura UCAV] {{Wayback|url=http://www.aviationweek.com/Article.aspx?id=%2Farticle-xml%2FAW_07_16_2012_p45-471464.xml |date=20130419155015 }} July 16, 2012</ref>和[[印度海軍|印度海軍]]<ref name="#1"/>正在開發的[[無人戰鬥航空載具|無人戰鬥航空載具]]（UCAV），該項目設計工作主要是透過{{link-en|印度航空發展局|Aeronautical Development Agency}}（ADA）進行，並在細節上分開工作。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/site/Story/100966/India/india-developing-unmanned-combat-aerial-vehicle.html |title=India developing unmanned combat aerial vehicle |publisher=Indiatoday.intoday.in |date=2010-06-10 |accessdate=2012-01-28 |archive-date=2010-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100730041845/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/site/Story/100966/India/india-developing-unmanned-combat-aerial-vehicle.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

奧拉能夠攜帶[[導彈|導彈]]、[[炸彈|炸彈]]和[[精确制导武器|精确制导武器]]，定位與法國的[[神经元无人作战飞机|神经元无人作战飞机]]、英國的[[雷神无人机|雷神无人机]]和美國的[[X-47A飞马试验机|X-47A飞马试验机]]大致相同。

== 概述 ==
根據{{link-en|印度航空發展局|Aeronautical Development Agency}}的描述，奧拉是一種具有武器發射能力的自衛（self-defending）高速（high-speed）偵察（reconnaissance）無人機。<ref>{{cite web |author=India joins bat-wing large UAV club |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/blogs/the-dewline/2010/06/india-joins-bat-wing-large-uav.html |title=India joins bat-wing large UAV club |publisher=[[Flightglobal.com|Flightglobal.com]] |date=2010-06-18 |accessdate=2012-01-28 |archive-date=2012-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026121030/http://www.flightglobal.com/blogs/the-dewline/2010/06/india-joins-bat-wing-large-uav.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>而其中所發布的一張圖片也顯示了奧拉是一種具有[[隱形戰機|隱形]]能力的無人機。後來根據印度國防研究與開發組織的帕拉德博士說法，奧拉能夠以30,001英尺的高空中飛行，並且攜帶不超過15噸重的導彈、炸彈和精確制導彈藥。

2015年，印度國防部長馬諾哈爾·帕里卡爾（Manohar Parrikar）通知[[联邦院_(印度)|印度聯邦院]]奧拉將採用國產的無後燃<ref>{{cite web |url=http://defenceradar.com/2014/04/24/aura-future-indian-airforce/ |title=AURA , The Future of Indian Airforce |publisher=Defence Radar |date=24 April 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150507030816/http://defenceradar.com/2014/04/24/aura-future-indian-airforce/ |archivedate=2015年5月7日 |access-date=2016年7月17日 }}</ref>版本的{{link-en|卡佛裡發動機|GTRE GTX-35VS Kaveri}}。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/pti-stories/indigenous-kaveri-engine-to-power-unmanned-combat-aircraft-115073001331_1.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-07-17 |archive-date=2019-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129043644/https://www.business-standard.com/article/pti-stories/indigenous-kaveri-engine-to-power-unmanned-combat-aircraft-115073001331_1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>同年11月13日，有媒體報導印度政府將撥款3000億印度盧比以用於一種名為「Ghatak」基於卡佛裡發動機基礎開發的發動機。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/defence/government-set-to-clear-rs-3000-crore-plan-to-develop-engine-for-indias-first-ucav/articleshow/49775096.cms |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-07-17 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031230/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/defence/government-set-to-clear-rs-3000-crore-plan-to-develop-engine-for-indias-first-ucav/articleshow/49775096.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>

